<i>verb</i>: 겉핥다 [거탈따] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>겉핥다 [거탈따]</dt><br>
<dd>have a superficial knowledge; smatter</dd><br>
<dd>내용을 제대로 파악하지 않고 대충대충 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To attain a less than substantial understanding of a topic while seeking to sound or appear knowledgeable.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>